high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the kitchen table.
Pick up the knife on the kitchen table.
Cut the tomato on the table into slices.
Turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk forward and turn right to face the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the table.
Turn right and walk forward to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Take a step to the right to face the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a tomato slice and place it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the wall, then turn right again and go to the table across from you.
Pick up the knife in front of the coffee pot, on the table.
Cut the tomato on the table, in front of the coffee maker, into slices.
Turn to your right and go to the sink across from you.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk back across the room and turn to the table on your right.
Pick up one of the tomato slices, on the table.
Turn to your right and go across the kitchen, then to the microwave, on the counter top to the left of the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the tomato slice from the microwave.
Move over to your right, so that you are in front of the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the sink, to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a warm tomato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the table.
Take the large knife from the table.
Cut the tomato on the table into slices.
Turn right, go forward to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around, go forward to the wall, turn right to the table.
Take a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn right, go forward to the sink, turn left.
Cooke the slice of tomato in the microwave. Take the slice of tomato from the microwave.
Turn right to face the sink.
Put the slice of tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of tomato in a sink.
